class CMySocket : public CAsyncSocket{ // Attributespublic: // Operationspublic: CMySocket(); virtual ~CMySocket(); // Overridespublic: void SetParent(CDialog* pWnd);protected: virtual void OnSend(int nErrorCode); virtual void OnReceive(int nErrorCode); virtual void OnClose(int nErrorCode); virtual void OnConnect(int nErrorCode); virtual void OnAccept(int nErrorCode);private: CDialog* m_pWnd;};
